Package: my-bpf-sensor
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libbpf1 (>= 1.0.0)
Recommends: linux-image-$(flat-modules:=$(KERNEL_RELEASE)) | linux-image-generic
Description: CO-RE eBPF process exec sensor packaged for APT
 This package demonstrates how to bundle a CO-RE (Compile Once - Run Everywhere)
 eBPF program in a Debian package. It traces process exec events using an eBPF
 program loaded via libbpf's CO-RE skeleton, making it compatible across
 different kernel versions without recompilation.